rows.label: tev031401_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev031401_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Lulladu about his shop.

rows.label: tev031401_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev031401_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Lulladu if he's heard any interesting rumors.

rows.label: tev031401_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Lulladu about the Ganglion attack.

rows.label: tev031401_SEL0051
rows.name: Ask Lulladu about the Zu Pharg.

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0001
rows.name:
I think I need more stimulation, you know?
It's really rather boring out here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0002
rows.name:
Well, I decided to open up a repair shop since I enjoy
tinkering with things, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0003
rows.name:
And I wanted to open it in Armory Alley, but the rent
there is is just obscene...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0004
rows.name:
Instead I opened this location, since the rent was zero.
But you know what else is zero here? Customers.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0005
rows.name:
Maybe someday I'll be lucky enough to have a
fascinating xeno or two wander by and talk to me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0010
rows.name:
While I was in Oblivia, I was monitoring lifeforms in
various places, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0011
rows.name:
I also picked up a couple of very interesting
signatures in the region where this city is.
I think you call it Primordia?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0012
rows.name:
One of the lifeforms is clearly human, but the
other... Well, I guess I don't really know what it is?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0013
rows.name:
Still, if you place enough data probes, maybe you can
stumble upon it yourself?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0020
rows.name:
I saw Qmoevas and puges and pugiliths... 
Goodness me, don't the Ganglion have so many
marvelous weapons?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0021
rows.name:
I should have snuck onto the battlefield with the BLADEs
instead of taking cover on that blasted ship, right?
Now I'll never get a closer look at them![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0022
rows.name:
Er, why are you looking at me like that?
You don't think I'm just trying to satisfy some
sick curiosity, do you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0023
rows.name:
We need to...uh...to KNOW our enemy in order to
vanquish them, right? So I was just trying to do a little
field reconnaissance?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0030
rows.name:
I'm glad you asked, because I was hoping for a chance
to maybe talk someone's ear off about it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0031
rows.name:
Frankly, it's shocking they have the the technology to
keep an object of that size floating in place,
don't you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0032
rows.name:
And did I even mention the weaponry it was equipped
with? Goodness, but when the Ganglion get serious,
we'd all better watch out...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0033
rows.name:
Still, wouldn't you think its size works directly against
its mobility? So I guess that means it's not perfect?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Lulladu about recent developments.

rows.label: tev031401_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Lulladu about recent developments.

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0201
rows.name: Well, um...Troylan won't stop sending me voltant?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0202
rows.name:
I think someone gave him the idea that I'm in love with
the stuff somehow?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0203
rows.name:
I'm almost neck-deep in voltant at this point!
What am I going to to to do?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0204
rows.name:
I know I caused my share of trouble, and I do want to
make it up to Chiromyl, you know? But still...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031401_MSG0205
rows.name:
At this rate, I'll be buried so so deep in voltant that I
fear no one will know where it ends and I begin, right?[ST:wait ]
